      <h3>Effective Rate of Stacked Discounts</h3>
      <p>
        When a coupon is layered on top of an existing sale, the effective total discount is <em>always less than the two rates added together</em>. Keep this reference chart in mind when deciding whether a stacked-coupon deal is better than a single larger discount elsewhere.
